{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/instant-eyedropper-the-colour-picker-tool-i-ve-been-missing/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"I came across this today, and I wanted to share it as this is the first time I’ve found a simple, minimalistic eyedropper tool that allows me to get the HEX…","html":"<p>I came across this today, and I wanted to share it as this is the first time I’ve found a simple, minimalistic eyedropper tool that allows me to get the HEX value (or another variety of colur value) of any colour that is on my screen.</p>\n<p>Oh, and it’s freeware from SpiceBrains.</p>\n<p>One you install it, you get this added to your system tray.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 281px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2940084eba412126e4baef2d0139c5b5/6b1e2/blog_instanteyedropper_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.0126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"blog instanteyedropper 1\"\n        title=\"blog instanteyedropper 1\"\n        src=\"/static/2940084eba412126e4baef2d0139c5b5/6b1e2/blog_instanteyedropper_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2940084eba412126e4baef2d0139c5b5/c26ae/blog_instanteyedropper_1.png 158w,\n/static/2940084eba412126e4baef2d0139c5b5/6b1e2/blog_instanteyedropper_1.png 281w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 281px) 100vw, 281px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Then you click and hold the mouse button down to have this display appear by your cursor.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 275px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5e041752f0e0aaf9cce146a0a4b80970/6b2ea/blog_instanteyedropper_2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.0379746835443%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"blog instanteyedropper 2\"\n        title=\"blog instanteyedropper 2\"\n        src=\"/static/5e041752f0e0aaf9cce146a0a4b80970/6b2ea/blog_instanteyedropper_2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5e041752f0e0aaf9cce146a0a4b80970/c26ae/blog_instanteyedropper_2.png 158w,\n/static/5e041752f0e0aaf9cce146a0a4b80970/6b2ea/blog_instanteyedropper_2.png 275w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 275px) 100vw, 275px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Continuing to hold, point the crosshairs onto the color you want on your screen and then let go of the mouse button. Now the code display disappears, but you have the value saved in the clipboard.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 485px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/10017646ebce886bf8c51f7c4264dff1/44c61/blog_instanteyedropper_3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.810126582278485%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"blog instanteyedropper 3\"\n        title=\"blog instanteyedropper 3\"\n        src=\"/static/10017646ebce886bf8c51f7c4264dff1/44c61/blog_instanteyedropper_3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/10017646ebce886bf8c51f7c4264dff1/c26ae/blog_instanteyedropper_3.png 158w,\n/static/10017646ebce886bf8c51f7c4264dff1/6bdcf/blog_instanteyedropper_3.png 315w,\n/static/10017646ebce886bf8c51f7c4264dff1/44c61/blog_instanteyedropper_3.png 485w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 485px) 100vw, 485px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Easy, peezy, lemon squeezy.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>I know that there are a million or so of these kinds of apps out there. My favourite being the one built into the Internet Explorer F12 developer tools. But, this one lets you go outside of the browser window easily, and does exactly what I need it to do. Also, it’s out of the way, but always readily accessible.</p>\n<p>Great tool. You should download it.</p>\n<p>End Scene. </p>\n<p>~ DW</p>","fields":{"slug":"/blog/instant-eyedropper-the-colour-picker-tool-i-ve-been-missing/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Instant Eyedropper: The Colour Picker Tool I've Been Missing","tags":["internet explorer","ie"],"categories":["development"],"date":"August 20, 2013","description":null,"excerpt":"I came across this today, and I wanted to share it as this is the first time I've found a simple, minimalistic eyedropper tool that allows me to get the HEX value (or another variety of colur value) of any colour that is on my screen.","social_image":null}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"HTML Gaming for Core Gamers"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/html-gaming-for-core-gamers/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Picking The Technology for my Game"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/picking-the-technology-for-my-game/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/instant-eyedropper-the-colour-picker-tool-i-ve-been-missing/","prevSlug":"/blog/html-gaming-for-core-gamers/","nextSlug":"/blog/picking-the-technology-for-my-game/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2555585279","2841359383","3159585216"]}